title: The Lycan Wars:Revised Edition - Janet MacDonald [Paranormial Er
description:
The Lycan Wars: revised edition. Victor Feral steals the only daughter of his enemy. A rare She-wolf, Mica will not only secure the future of his dying pack but also prevent her father from encroaching on Feral territory-At least that was the plan. Mica claims Victor-or at least her wolf side did. In doing so she sets a war in motion that may very well wipe out her entire race.
